result.formatted_address: Hong Kong Skycity Marriott Hotel, 1 Sky City Rd E, Chek Lap Kok, Hong Kong
result.name: Man Ho Chinese Restaurant

reviews.text: Nice dimsums. Great service.

Visited Man Ho Chinese Restaurant twice with my family in Feb 2019.
The standard of Chinese food served right here is outstanding.
The atmosphere is so relaxed and quiet, not the common adjectives to describe a Chinese Restaurant (normally it’s very lively, loud and crowded when you engage in ‘Yum Cha’)
The table we sat looked over to the newly built Boundary Crossing Terminal for the Macau Zhuhai Bridge, charming to look at from a distance.
Dishes we ordered include: Peking Duck, Steamed Fish on Floater Leaf, Tantan Noodles, Sesame Rice Balls etc.
The waiting service is also exceptionally attentive and welcoming.
Prices to dine here will exceed HKD$200/person, but you can get discounts as a club Marriott member.

Highly recommend visiting :)

result.formatted_address: Hong Kong Skycity Marriott Hotel, 1 Sky City Rd E, Chek Lap Kok, Hong Kong
result.name: Hong Kong SkyCity Marriott Hotel

reviews.text: This hotel is great. Good access to the airport and the train to the rest of HK. Nice views. Modern and clean rooms. Multiple good food options on site. Free shuttle to and from airport every 30 minutes.

Lovely and close to the airport with a pool and gym very easy to get to! Free shuttle from the airport to hotel - very helpful and friendly staff with a nice restaurant and bar in the lobby! The room was spacious with a big bathroom and TV and had lovely air conditioning

Decent airport hotel. Lots of travellers and airline crews. I got a room on the club floor which was recently renovated and met expectations. The executive lounge had been relocated to the ground floor due to renovations. Decent food for dinner and breakfast.

Good business hotel for a quick stay. Nice executive lounge available. Rooms are clean and beds are comfortable. Light sleepers do ask for rooms facing the sea. 

Theres free shuttle service to Shopping Outlet and very convenient to MTR station too.

Staff was friendly and welcoming. Rooms are nice and clean. Location is very close to the airport, which is perfect for an overnight layover. Overall a very nice hotel. This was a perfect short stay in Hong Kong for us.

result.name: 香港天際萬豪酒店

reviews.text: 吃喝玩樂很齊全👍

香港天際萬豪酒店就在香港國際機場的旁邊，雖然是在旁邊不過還是建議乘坐飯店的接駁車往返香港機場與飯店之間，接駁車的上車地點就在國際機場的1號停車場種的11號跟12號閘口，每半個小時就會有一班車從機場到飯店，這次入住的房間剛好面向機場，所以可以看到飛機起降，飯店內的健身房為24小時，行政酒廊從六點就開始營運，但是早餐則是6:30才開始，如果是要搭早班飛機的乘客，最早五點就有接駁車到機場，這間的飯店走廊比較長，如果是在走廊底的房間從電梯口走到房間是需要一點時間的，不過房間內的擺設非常的整齊且乾淨，是一次非常愉快的入住經驗

This hotel is great. Good access to the airport and the train to the rest of HK. Nice views. Modern and clean rooms. Multiple good food options on site. Free shuttle to and from airport every 30 minutes.

Lovely and close to the airport with a pool and gym very easy to get to! Free shuttle from the airport to hotel - very helpful and friendly staff with a nice restaurant and bar in the lobby! The room was spacious with a big bathroom and TV and had lovely air conditioning

result.formatted_address: Hong Kong International Airport (HKG), 1 Sky Plaza Rd, Chek Lap Kok, Hong Kong
result.name: Hong Kong International Airport

reviews.text: On the whole a very good airport. Security is quick and efficient, and passport control is normally very quick too. There are a good selection of places to eat, despite ongoing renovations. The internal transit system is easy to use. No complaints.

One of the Large airports in the world. Its very wonderful shape of airport. Staffs are so friendly and helpful to passengers. The airport is very clean and fully well maintained. The view of airport is incredible. My experience was great here...

Great airport in town. Large varieties of food and great service at the Check In counter. Fast passenger flow. The terminals are large and comfy as well. The problems are the food can be quite expensive, and you may expect to walk a lot inside the airport. Also, it is far from Downtown, so you may catch a taxi or hop onto the Airport Express. Still pretty great tho. 4/5

Incredible!!! One of the amazing airports in the world. I don't know how it comes to their mind to build up an airport like this place. Its very big and wonderful shape airport. Staffs are so friendly and helpful to passengers. The airport is very clean and fully well maintained. The view of airport is incredible. My experience was great here. I was totally surprised. Love it❤

One of the best airports I have ever been. I fell in love with their relaxation corner in terminal 1. They are silent with ambient temperature and smooth lights. Even the room is perfumed with a soft smell of eucalyptus. They even have charging ports right next to the comfortable beds. With an amazing view of aircraft through the glass wall on one side.
